## Cursor-Specific

### Skills

Invoke via `@skill-name`. Index: [`.genai/skills/README.md`](../../.genai/skills/README.md). Language/stack conventions load automatically via glob-scoped rules.

### Review Agents + MCP

Review-delivery agents live in `.cursor/agents/`. Richer MCP surfaces arrive in later layers.

### Commands

Slash commands live in `.cursor/commands/`. See the **Commands** table above (from `core.md`) for intent-based lookup.

Plans, when present, live in `.cursor/plans/**/*.plan.md`.
